x_n
x_n = \sum_{i=1}^n \frac{1}{i} 
x_{n+1}-x_n =\sum_{i=1}^{n+1} \frac{1}{i}-\sum_{i=1}^n \frac{1}{i} =\frac{1}{n+1}
